room_title: Escape room "Party @ Grandma’s House" by MindBreak in St. Louis
room_description:
Grandma is a little prankster. She invites you over to her house for a party, but everything is missing! Where are the Cupcakes or Cookies? Where are the Napkins and Plates? What about if you get thirsty? Nothing is to be found. You notice some clues, some locks… Is grandma playing a game with you? She sure is!

And it will be a lot of fun, if you and your friends can figure it out. You get One Hour to “Escape with your treats” and enjoy the party!
